Posts.Content: ls1229 wrote: Hi I had a screening mammogram that came back last week with breast density and architectural deformity with spiculated margin. I have been called back for diagnostic mammogram, ultrasound and meeting with radiologist. The earliest they can get me in is next week, and I have made the mistake of googling while waiting. Articles I've read state that 1/2 to 2/3 of women with this finding have a malignancy. I also have a family history of breast cancer ( mom ) Does anyone here have personal experience with these particular findings ?  Or ideas on how to get through another weekend of worrying without going crazy :-)  Thanks for reading.  Log in to post a reply
Posts.Title: Can't stop worrying and googling ls1229 Cat123

Posts.Content: Feb 1, 2012 06:41PM ls1229 wrote: Thank you to all of you.  I really appreciate it.  I am going to try to stay away from Google for the next week anyway !!  Great ideas on the diversional activities.   I will definitely keep you posted.   You all are a great group of support and resources.
